Description: Payment to fund the department's client's deposit account controlled by Gallagher Bassett International Limited, on the department's behalf. The funds are provided and owned by the Department for Education to meet claims in respect of academy trusts that have joined the department's Risk Protection Arrangement (RPA). Payments for claims over £25,000 are included in this dataset. At no point are the funds owned by Gallagher Bassett International Limited.
